{"tid":1237901,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)邊個殺我隻狗1-2","createTime":"2019-06-17T16:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T20:33:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f77e5b970bde252118e0d225166eda8084e995bf","tid":1237901,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=a81082f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=3e2fcf6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5314d4f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg&h=62ceec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.約翰&middot;維克是一位退隱江湖的殺手，不久前失去了因病而逝的妻子海倫，這令他哀傷不已，舉辦完葬禮後連過去同為殺手的馬克斯也前來關心他。不久後，約翰收到了一隻海倫生前為他訂的小狗黛西，海倫希望黛西能陪伴約翰，而他也將黛西視為朋友。一早，約翰開著他69年的福特野馬愛車和黛西出門，當到一間加油站加油時，塔拉索夫家族的領頭維果的兒子約謝夫想要和約翰買下他的車，但被約翰拒絕，約謝夫便此心生不滿。當晚，約謝夫和另外兩位朋友格雷戈里、維克多蒙面闖入約翰家中，不但襲擊了他還殺死了黛西..<br />\n<br />\n2.在前殺手約翰&middot;維克殺光維果和約謝夫&middot;塔拉索夫一行人的四天後，約翰開始尋找自己遭到前者搶走的1969年福特野馬，並循跡發現車在維果的弟弟艾倫那裡。約翰在獲得艾倫根據地的門卡後隨即開車前往，並與艾倫的手下們展開飛車追逐及搏鬥，而艾倫也察覺到傳說中「殺神」的到來；在他打倒其手下後，約翰到艾倫的辦公室倒了兩杯酒給他，以示「和平」。接著約翰便開車回家，與自己在殺死維果後帶回家的「沒有取名」狗見面..<br />\n<br />\n12 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有心情就播埋3<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4dc1cffb\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=fbf8b546\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef82d7df8838f96c4ad8805fe8045833dc96b1e8","tid":1237901,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97aefd38704b393a05ad677cc0c30e8778a83447","tid":1237901,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b03445e2b67420d2bf5287c51991cdf975164e9","tid":1237901,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"